---
title: Smart Korean-Inspired Pork Salad with Creamy Sesame Dressing
description: This bountiful salad is bursting with colour, Korean-inspired flavours and wholesome veggies! Spicy, soy-infused pork and creamy, gochujang-based dressing round out the plate for a delicious, light way to start your week.

